796
00:49:56,360 --> 00:49:59,352
Did you know that
a hippopotamus chooses one mate

797
00:49:59,720 --> 00:50:01,676
and they stay together for life?

798
00:50:03,080 --> 00:50:03,990
Did you know that?

799
00:50:05,360 --> 00:50:06,076
No.

800
00:50:08,080 --> 00:50:09,354
Isn't that marvelous?

801
00:50:16,520 --> 00:50:17,430
This is it?

802
00:50:18,280 --> 00:50:19,599
- He lives here?
