In our image of women.

817
00:50:58,480 --> 00:50:59,799
Yeah, that's true.

818
00:51:14,920 --> 00:51:16,717
<i>So I finally finished a new draft.</i>

819
00:51:17,080 --> 00:51:19,878
<i>But France TV</i>
<i>had a little surprise for me.</i>

820
00:51:22,000 --> 00:51:24,673
<i>They said that</i>
<i>an Australian satellite "bouquet"...</i>

821
00:51:25,040 --> 00:51:26,268
