822
00:51:26,640 --> 00:51:30,758
TS6 is a silent partner of PassionTV,
through Eurosat 2000.

823
00:51:31,800 --> 00:51:32,596
<i>Yeah, that's it.</i>

824
00:51:32,960 --> 00:51:36,669
<i>It was some sort of "bouquet" buy-out</i>
<i>by God knows who.</i>

825
00:51:37,800 --> 00:51:42,351
<i>Anyway,</i> Love Passion in Venice
<i>was now a BBC 2 co-production.</i>

826
00:51:42,720 --> 00:51:44,278
<i>So the script had to be in English.</i>

827
00:51:44,800 --> 00:51:45,516
Oh, really?

828
00:51:46,240 --> 00:51:48,834
<i>Their BBC counterparts are currently</i>

829
00:51:49,200 --> 00:51:53,557
<i>putting together a pool</i>
<i>of screenwriters. And so, that's that.</i>

830
00:51:54,120 --> 00:51:58,716
Sorry. We know how much you've
invested in <i>Love Passion in Venice.</i>

831
00:51:59,200 --> 00:52:03,159
<i>He said, "Those are</i>
<i>the vagaries of globalization. "</i>

832
00:52:03,840 --> 00:52:05,592
You're a victim of globalization.

833
00:52:06,080 --> 00:52:07,308
<i>That made me feel better.</i>

834
00:52:07,880 --> 00:52:09,996
Hold on, I speak English.

835
00:52:13,600 --> 00:52:14,555
Meaning?

836
00:52:15,240 --> 00:52:17,674
