857
00:55:44,080 --> 00:55:45,638
Thank you, William.

858
00:55:48,320 --> 00:55:49,196
Bye.

859
00:56:03,760 --> 00:56:04,795
<i>So, there it is.</i>

860
00:56:05,160 --> 00:56:07,469
<i>A love story is above all a story.</i>

861
00:56:56,880 --> 00:56:57,869
